OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FRuben Amorim will take charge as
OL,7,FManchester United's manager in just
OL,8,Funder two weeks, and has quite a task
OL,9,Fon his hands as he tries to live up to
OL,10,FSir Alex Ferguson's legacy, ITV News
OL,11,FSports Editor Steve Scott reports
OL,13,FThe England manager's role has long
OL,14,Fbeen described as the 'impossible job'
OL,15,Fbut recent evidence suggests that
OL,16,Flabel should actually apply to whoever
OL,17,Fis in charge at Manchester United.
