OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FAmorim's appointment is of course the
OL,7,Fmost significant decision made by the
OL,8,FIneos executive team since they took
OL,9,Fcontrol of all things football earlier
OL,10,Fthis year.
OL,12,FA statement released on Friday said
OL,13,FAmorim has signed a contract until
OL,14,FJune 2027 with a club option of an
OL,15,Fadditional year.
OL,17,FHe will join Manchester United on
OL,18,FNovember 11 once he has fulfilled his
OL,19,Fobligations with Sporting CP and Ruud
OL,20,Fvan Nistelrooy will continue to take
OL,21,Fcharge of the team until Ruben joins.
