OL,6,FSo changing their minds so soon
OL,7,Fafterwards has been costly and is an
OL,8,Funcomfortable look for Sir Jim, who
OL,9,Fhas been cost cutting in every
OL,10,Fdepartment at Old Trafford.
OL,12,FFrom Sir Alex's ambassadorial deal to
OL,13,Fhundreds of job losses and company
OL,14,Fcredit cards being cancelled, amongst
OL,15,Fmany other measures - no one has been
OL,16,Fsafe from the Ineos guillotine.
OL,18,FAmorim's curtain raiser will be away
OL,19,Fat newly promoted - and winless -
OL,20,FIpswich.
