OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FNot only will this be his first match
OL,7,Fin his new role, it will also be his
OL,8,Ffirst match as manager of a club
OL,9,Foutside Portugal.
OL,11,FHe has a good reputation having led
OL,12,FSporting to their first league title
OL,13,Fin 19 years, and subsequently repeated
OL,14,Fthat feat, along with capturing a
OL,15,Fcouple of Portuguese Cup trophies, all
OL,16,Finside four years.
