OL,3,CRuben Amorim takes on 'impossible job'
OL,4,Cof Manchester United manager
OL,6,FBut the Primeira Liga is not the
OL,7,FPremier League, despite the fact that
OL,8,FAmorim attracted interest from West
OL,9,FHam United and reportedly Manchester
OL,10,FCity too for post-Guardiola.
OL,12,FThe past weeks have played out like
OL,13,Fsomething of a soap opera, so the
OL,14,FIpswich game can't come soon enough.
OL,16,FBy January we should be able to assess
OL,17,Fhow shrewd the choice of Amorim has
OL,18,Fbeen, and by extension whether finally
OL,19,Fthe Ineos era will have provided
OL,20,FUnited fans with something to shout
OL,21,Fabout.
