OL,6,FManchester United's statement in full
OL,8,FManchester United is delighted to
OL,9,Fannounce the appointment of Ruben
OL,10,FAmorim as Head Coach of the men's
OL,11,Ffirst team, subject to work visa
OL,12,Frequirements.
OL,14,FHe will join until June 2027 with a
OL,15,Fclub option of an additional year once
OL,16,Fhe has fulfilled his obligations to
OL,17,Fhis current club. He will join
OL,18,FManchester United on Monday 11
OL,19,FNovember.
