OL,6,FRuben is one of the most exciting and
OL,7,Fhighly rated young coaches in European
OL,8,Ffootball. Highly decorated as both a
OL,9,Fplayer and coach, his titles include
OL,10,Fwinning the Primeira Liga twice in
OL,11,FPortugal with Sporting CP; the first
OL,12,Fof which was the club's first title in
OL,13,F19 years.
